ringswitchEthernetIfOperMaxFrameSize.name: ringswitchEthernetIfOperMaxFrameSize
ringswitchEthernetIfOperMaxFrameSize.description: The maximum frame size currently used on the Ethernet or Gigabit port. For 10/100 Ethernet this value can only be 1514. For Gigabit other larger values are supported for jumbo frames.

ringswitchEthernetXBDupAddrTable.name: ringswitchEthernetXBDupAddrTable
ringswitchEthernetXBDupAddrTable.description: This table duplicate mac address information

ringswitchEthernetXBDupAddrEntry.name: ringswitchEthernetXBDupAddrEntry
ringswitchEthernetXBDupAddrEntry.description: A list of duplicate mac addresses for each Ethernet port in the rsw

ringswitchEthernetXBDupAddrIfIndex.name: ringswitchEthernetXBDupAddrIfIndex
ringswitchEthernetXBDupAddrIfIndex.description: The value of this object identifies the ethernet interface for which this entry contains management information. The value of this object for a particular interface has the same value as the ifIndex object for the same interface.

ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsTable.name: ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsTable
ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsTable.description: This table contains information relating to the forwarding statistics that are maintained by each ethernet interface acting as a translational bridge to Token-ring.

ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsEntry.name: ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsEntry
ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsEntry.description: A list of information relating to the forwarding statistics of a single ethernet interface acting as a translational bridge to Token-ring.

ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsIfIndex.name: ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsIfIndex
ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsIfIndex.description: The value of this object identifies the ethernet interface for which this entry contains management information. The value of this object for a particular interface has the same value as the ifIndex object for the same interface.

ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsDiscSptEnc.name: ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsDiscSptEncapsBlock
ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsDiscSptEnc.description: The number of received frames discarded by this interface because the encasulated spanning tree detected a 3rd party bridge loop and has forced blocking. These frames will be counted in forwarding statistics even though the frame is discarded.

ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsDiscFilter.name: ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsDiscFilter
ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsDiscFilter.description: The number of received frames discarded by this interface because the DA was known to be on Ethernet.

ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsDiscBPDU.name: ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsDiscBPDU
ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsDiscBPDU.description: The number of BPDU's received from Ethernet which have been discarded (i.e. not received) by this interface because they could not be encapsulated (e.g. because they are too big). Only counted when encapsulated SPT is enabled.

ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsDiscBPDUEn.name: ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsDiscBPDUEncaps
ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsDiscBPDUEn.description: The number of received encapsulated BPDU frames discarded by this interface because they are invalid or duplicates. Only counted when encapsulated SPT is enabled.

ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsDiscTag802.name: ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsDiscTag8021qCfi
ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsDiscTag802.description: The number of received frames discarded by this interface because they are 802.1Q encapsulated Token Ring frames.

ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsDiscTag802.name: ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsDiscTag8021qVlan
ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsDiscTag802.description: The number of received frames discarded by this interface because they have an 802.1Q tag with the wrong VLAN id. Only counted when ethernet tagging is enabled.

ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsDiscBadRif.name: ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsDiscBadRif
ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsDiscBadRif.description: The number of received frames discarded by this interface because a non-cached RIF is invalid.

ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsDiscHopLim.name: ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsDiscHopLimit
ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsDiscHopLim.description: The number of received frames discarded by this interface because a non-cached RIF is longer than the hop-count limit.

ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsDiscDuplic.name: ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsDiscDuplicateRin
ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsDiscDuplic.description: The number of received frames discarded by this interface because a non-cached RIF contains the interface's ring number twice.

ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsDiscIPDisa.name: ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsDiscIPDisabled
ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsDiscIPDisa.description: The number of received frames discarded by this interface because IP forwarding is disabled.

ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsDiscARPDis.name: ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsDiscARPDisabled
ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsDiscARPDis.description: The number of received ARP and RARP frames discarded by this interface because IP forwarding is disabled.

ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsDiscNCPCac.name: ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsDiscNCPCache
ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsDiscNCPCac.description: The number of received NCP requests discarded by this interface because they could not be cached.

ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsDiscIPXDis.name: ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsDiscIPXDisabled
ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsDiscIPXDis.description: The number of received frames discarded by this interface because IPX forwarding is disabled.

ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsDiscIPXTyp.name: ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsDiscIPXTypeSnap
ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsDiscIPXTyp.description: The number of received IPX SNAP frames discarded by this interface because SNAP encapsulation is not selected on this interface.

ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsDiscIPXTyp.name: ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsDiscIPXType8022
ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsDiscIPXTyp.description: The number of received 802.2 IPX frames discarded by this interface because 802.2 encapsulation is not selected on this interface.

ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsDiscIPXTyp.name: ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsDiscIPXType8023
ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsDiscIPXTyp.description: The number of received 802.3 IPX frames discarded by this interface because 802.3 encapsulation is not selected on this interface.

ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsDiscIPXTyp.name: ringswitchEthernetXBToTRNStatsDiscIPXTypeDix
